<%= render "shared_mailer/user", user: @sender %>
<h2 class="mb-10 main-title mt-4">Your sponsorship has been accepted!</h2>
<p class="w-full mb-6 primary-3 paragraph">
  Great news! <%= @sender.name %> has accepted your sponsorship request on Talent Protocol. You are now officially sponsoring their journey, supporting their growth, and helping them unlock new opportunities.
</p>
<p class="w-full mb-3 primary-3 paragraph">
  We encourage you to stay engaged with everyone you support and their work. This connection can create a mutually beneficial relationship, fostering collaboration and growth for both of you.
</p>
<p class="w-full mb-6 primary-3 paragraph">
  Thank you for being an active participant in the Talent Protocol community. Your support makes a significant impact on the lives and careers of talented individuals like <%= @sender.name %>.
</p>
<%= link_to "Check #{@sender.name}'s profile", user_url(username: @sender.username), class: "btn btn-primary fw-800 text-5xl py-4 mb-5 w-full", style: "width: 90%" %>
<p class="w-full mt-6 mb-3 primary-3 paragraph">
  If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.
</p>
<p class="w-full primary-3 paragraph">
  Let's do this,
  <br/>
  Talent Protocol team
</p>
